Author: MyPOS_failure_alt
Text: The pilot is very "look at this skinny chick she's so weird and won't eat anything, this large woman will help her." I guess it started at the end of heroin chic so maybe that's why

Author: Iscariiot
Text: I love that show but it really does seem like a “DONT BE FAT!!!” kinda deal. Even when they discuss anorexia it feels at a distance. Weird to know the pilot was different?
